<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">春风拂面而来，正是播种希望，守护花草的时节。伴随着植树节到来，江西软件职业技术大学经济管理学院开展了植树种花活动。2023年3月14日下午，28期入党积极分子在郭伟老师的带领下开展了加种植樱花树活动。让学员们用行动为环境添彩、添绿、添美，用情感与自然对话，在实践中发现美、守护美、创造美。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">来看看老师和同学们的辛勤成果吧！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713359926905004043.png" title="1713359926905004043.png" alt="image.png" width="561" height="315" style="width: 561px; height: 315px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">此次植树活动，不仅为学校增添了一道靓丽的风景线，同时也让大家得到了劳动锻炼，提升了党性修养，增强了生态环保意识，坚定了“绿水青山就是金山银山”的发展理念，筑牢了保护环境的责任感和使命感。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-shadow: none; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">书是人类进步的阶梯，绿是充满生机的色彩。将旧书回收用于完善学生读书角，不仅能将知识传播到更多人手里，而且让我们更加懂得书本和树木的宝贵。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-shadow: none; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713359986346039370.png" title="1713359986346039370.png" alt="image.png" width="683" height="450" style="width: 683px; height: 450px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; line-height: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-shadow: none; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">植树造林不仅可以绿化和美化家园，同时还可以起到扩大山林资源、防止水土流失、保护农田、调节气候、促进经济发展等作用，是一项建设美丽校园、优化环境的工程。</span></p><p><br/></p>